Class BeaconInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.sdk.cloud.model.BeaconInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class BeaconInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Immutable representation of beacon's information stored in Estimote Cloud. If you want to mutate your can use BeaconInfo.Builder object or invoke builder() on existing object.
